title: Facebook says employee death was suicide
text: The tech company issued the statement after numerous people gathered outside the company's headquarters on Thursday to demand "justice for Qin."

title: Launch of Facebook's Libra could be delayed over regulatory concerns: executive
text: The launch of Facebook's Libra could be pushed back to tackle the regulatory concerns that have been raised around the world, the head of the organization set up to oversee the cryptocurrency told Reuters.

title: Libra Official Says Launch Date Depends on Discussions With Regulators
text: Sep.27 -- Bertrand Perez, chief operating officer at managing director at Libra Association, discusses efforts to launch the Libra digital currency and talks with global regulators.

title: Facebook Ups the Ante in VR With Oculus Horizon & More
text: Facebook (FB) boosts its virtual reality portfolio with Oculus offerings such as Facebook Horizon, Oculus Link, hand tracking features and more.

title: Facebook-ICC Deal Spurs Competition in India Streaming Space
text: Facebook's (FB) ICC deal is expected to help expand its footprint in India's streaming space, currently dominated by Disney's Hotstar and SonyLiv.

title: Facebook execs talk user privacy and content moderation
text: Yahoo Finance's Andy Serwer speaks to Monika Bickert Facebook Head of Global Policy Management, John Devine Vice President of Global Operations and Guy Rosen Vice President of Integrity about the challenges with content moderation policies and user privacy.

title: Sheryl Sandberg is in talks to testify on Facebook's cryptocurrency libra as soon as next month
text: Lawmakers have been skeptical of Facebook's plans to create a new cryptocurrency in the wake of privacy scandals.

title: Facebook's Libra project is a 'walled garden,' Ripple exec says
text: The proposed libra token will be managed by a Switzerland-based organization known as the Libra Association.
